## Setup

### Installation

Install `sqlfmt` from [Python Package Index](https://pypi.org/project/sqlfmt/):

```
pip install sqlfmt
```

Install `sqlfmt` from [Source Code](https://github.com/HH-MWB/sqlfmt):

```
python setup.py install
```


